                            <comment id="14575690" author="githubbot" created="Sat, 6 Jun 2015 11:07:50 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user andralungu opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/799&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/799&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-2178&quot; title=&quot;groupReduceOnNeighbors throws NoSuchElementException&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-2178&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-2178&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;gelly&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Fixed groupReduceOnNeighbors bug&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    This PR adds an iterator.hasNext() check in the groupReduceOnNeighbors method, fixing the NoSuchElementException bug reported in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-2178&quot; title=&quot;groupReduceOnNeighbors throws NoSuchElementException&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-2178&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-2178&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    @vasia , @StephanEwen, maybe we can merge this before the upcoming 0.9 release &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;

