                            <comment id="14585700" author="githubbot" created="Mon, 15 Jun 2015 09:31:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Github user vasia commented on the pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/799#issuecomment-111993642&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/799#issuecomment-111993642&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    @andralungu, I believe the same issue appears in `ApplyCoGroupFunctionOnAllEdges` and `ApplyCoGroupFunction`. Could you check if that&apos;s the case and fix those too if needed?&lt;br/&gt;
    Also, adding a test might be a good idea &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
